dev.sl4sh.polarity.games

Interface GameLobbyBase<T extends GameBase>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The lobby's associated GameBase object
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractGameLobby, SpleefLobby

    public interface GameLobbyBase<T extends GameBase>
    This interface is the base object for Polarity's game lobbies. No implementation is provided and it is recommended to inherit AbstractGameLobby instead if you want to create a game lobby
